Sure, here are some example sentences in Serbian that use the word "hodnik" in different forms and positions:

1. *Hodnik* je popločan pločicama. (The *hallway* is tiled.)
2. U *hodniku* je bilo jako hladno. (It was very cold in the *hallway*.)
3. Stavila je cipele u *hodniku*. (She put her shoes in the *hallway*.)
4. *Hodnikom* se čulo zveckanje ključeva. (The sound of keys jingling echoed through the *hallway*.)
5. Krenula je prema *hodniku*. (She headed towards the *hallway*.)
6. *Hodnici* su bili osvetljeni sijalicama. (The *hallways* were lit with light bulbs.)
7. Izašao je iz *hodnika* i ušao u sobu. (He left the *hallway* and entered the room.)
8. *Hodnik* vodi do kupatila. (The *hallway* leads to the bathroom.)

I hope this helps! Let me know if you have any other questions.